  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Support Associate",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Sales Support Associate</strong></h2><p>At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, this role is designed for individuals who want real exposure, real learning, and real responsibility from day one.<br />You’ll be supporting on-ground sales and brand engagement campaigns, working directly with people, and developing practical communication and marketing skills through hands-on experience.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Support face-to-face sales and customer engagement activities</p></li><li><p>Assist in representing client brands at events, roadshows, and outreach locations</p></li><li><p>Help deliver clear, professional brand messaging during customer interactions</p></li><li><p>Work closely with your team to support daily campaign objectives</p></li><li><p>Build practical skills in sales, communication, and customer engagement through on-the-job learning</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Full training provided — no prior experience required</p></li><li><p>Clear, performance-based development pathway</p></li><li><p>Exposure to different campaigns and working locations</p></li><li><p>Direct coaching, mentorship, and team support</p></li></ul><h3><strong>This Role Is Suitable For Individuals Who</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Are comfortable interacting with people or keen to develop this capability</p></li><li><p>Are reliable, proactive, and open to learning</p></li><li><p>Prefer active, on-the-ground work over desk-based roles</p></li><li><p>Can commit to a full-time role</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If you’re interested in building practical experience in sales support and customer engagement, we welcome your application.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
